To add a table of contents to a standalone page, include the following:    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/toc.min.css" />
    <script src="jquery-1.9.1.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="mousetrap.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="jquery.scrollTo-1.4.3.1-min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="toc.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

The "toc.js" file is slightly modified to automatically build the table of contents at start.  At the top of it are various options that may be modified.
